    <string name="dialog_greeting">Welcome</string>
    <string name="dialog_greeting_message">This app is still in its alpha state. This means:
        \n- You should not expect a fully tested and bug-free app.
        \n- Some commands and responses for some supported devices could be missing
        \n- Future releases can invalidate all your previous settings (I\'ll try to migrate settings if there are enough users).
        \n- Future releases might remove/change previous features.
        \n- Updates are not necessarily delivered on a regular basis.\n
        \nIf you find any bugs/issues or have suggestions on how to improve this app, feel free to email me (spiritcroc@gmail.com).\n
        \nThis app is open source and requires contributions to grow! If you want to help with development, you can view the code at https://github.com/SpiritCroc/Modular-Remote.\n
        \nCoding is not the only way to help: In order to natively support more TCP devices, command lists are required to include in this app. A guide to supporting new devices can be found here: https://github.com/SpiritCroc/Modular-Remote/blob/master/guide_supporting_new_devices.md
        \nAlso take a look at the to-do list, there should be a section called \'no coding required\':
        \nhttps://github.com/SpiritCroc/Modular-Remote/blob/master/TODO.txt\n
        \nThis program is distributed in the hope that it will be useful, but WITHOUT ANY WARRANTY; without even the implied warranty of MERCHANTABILITY or FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE. See the GNU General Public License for more details.</string>

